# @param {String} s
# @return {Integer}
def minimum_beautiful_substrings(s)
    return -1 if s[0] == '0'
    powers_of_5 = []
    i = 1
    while i.to_s(2).length <= s.length
        powers_of_5 << i.to_s(2)
        i *= 5
    end

    dp = [Float::INFINITY] * (s.length + 1)
    dp[0] = 0
    (1..s.length).each do |i|
        powers_of_5.each do |pow|
            len = pow.length
            if i >= len && s[i-len...i] == pow
                dp[i] = [dp[i], dp[i-len] + 1].min
            end
        end
    end

    dp[s.length] == Float::INFINITY ? -1 : dp[s.length]
end
